  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0dd3\u0dc3\u0dca \u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db8\u0dc4\u0dcf \u0db6\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0d85\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dd4\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Lees Truss to the Chair of Prime Minister of Great Britain",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "British Foreign Minister Liz Truss won the new Prime Minister post.",
        "She got 81,326 votes from Tory members, while Rishi Sunak got almost 60,399.",
        "Accordingly, 47-year-old Liz Truss became the prime minister after she became the party leader.",
        "The Prime Minister of Britain is held by the leader of the ruling party. Currently, the ruling party is the Conservative Party.",
        "The race for the leadership of the Conservative Party was between Liz Truss and Di Rishi Sunak.",
        "Rishi Sunak is the former Chancellor of the Exchequer. Rishi Sunak is of Indian origin. If he were to become British Prime Minister, Sunak would be the first Briton of Indian origin to hold the post.",
        "The party leader is elected by the party's internal vote. The poll was conducted among Conservative Party representatives, party activists and party members and the results were announced today.",
        "Accordingly, if Liz Truss wins the party leadership and becomes the Prime Minister, Liz Truss will be the third woman to become British Prime Minister after Theresa May and Margaret Thatcher."
      ],
